videos.title: Is It Possible to Play Momir in Brawl?  Much Abrew
videos.description:
Momir is an awesome format, but it's hard to find people to play against. Does Ornate Imitations let us play Momir in Brawl whenever we want? Let's find out!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
